Hotkey on F5:
Freeze.ahk Sourcefile
Freeze.exe Application
Reset timer: F9
Close app: F12

Hotkey on Numpad1 (Num pad, 1):
Freeze_Num1.ahk Sourcefile
Freeze_Num1.exe Application
Reset timer: NumEnter
Close app: NumSub (Minus, -)

Hotkey on Numpad4 (Num pad, 4):
Freeze_Num4.ahk Sourcefile
Freeze_Num4.exe Application
Reset timer: NumEnter
Close app: NumSub (Minus, -)